data.text:
If you grew up watching Disney channel like we did, you might have favored Vanessa (Anne) Hudgens or Ashley Tisdale. After all, they were rivals in High School Musical! Even though we love both, we thought it'd be a fun thought exercise to defend our personal favorites!

Say hello to my new American friend, Lizzie McGuire! We're finally back with the last installment of our discussion of the Lizzie McGuire Movie!!

We hope you enjoy and we will see you soon!

Get your gelato out because we are embarking on a trip to Rome! These next three weeks we are discussing the Lizzie McGuire movie starring (debatably) the QUEEN of Disney Channel, Hilary Duff. We hope you enjoy part 1 and even consider re-watching the movie along with us. It may be cold outside this part of the year, but this story will warm your heart.

Follow us on IG to know when new episodes come out!

IG: @wildchatspodcast

Tiffany's IG: @hi_tiff_

Sara's IG: @iamsaracarreras

WHAT TEAM? ...........WHAT TEAM????.........

After exactly one year of silence, the Wildchats are finally back and ready to get back to what we could never grow out of--talking about Disney Channel. This is just a bit up a catch up episode--a warm-up if you will, for what is to come. We hope you stay with us on this journey because life is amazing with you on the ride.

Uploading kinda late but anyway, this was our FIRST EVER live streamed episode! We recorded it back in december of last year. In this episode we discussed Disney Channel "it girl" Debby Ryan. You can find her in shows like Suite Life on Deck and Jessie. She even inspired one of Tik Tok's classic memes from her performance of Radio Rebel. She's quirky, she's fun...and you guys are too! We loved talking and reacting with you all on Youtube. See you for the next one!

IGs:

It's the last episode of Camp Wildchats (So Hot Summer)! And what better way to end it than by watching Camp Rock? We're talking Demi, we're talking the Jonas Brothers, we're talking HOT TUNES TV CHINA! So turn on that radio as loud as it can go and listen to our latest episode! It's ReAlLY gOoD!

Today on the podcast we analyze Hannah Montana's two greatest loves, Jake and Jesse. Who was the better boyfriend? Who did Miley REALLY deserve? Who COULD be the one? So many questions. In the episode we also responded to your comments on our Instagram! Enjoy!
